metadata.name: Fantasy World 1
metadata.description:
The City of Rebots and Humans is a place where two very different species coexist in harmony. Humans and rebots live and work together, sharing their skills and knowledge to create a thriving community. The city is a marvel of engineering and architecture, with towering skyscrapers and sprawling parks. It is divided into different districts, each with its own unique character and purpose.

 Rebots are humanoid robots that were created to serve humans in various capacities. They are programmed to perform tasks such as cleaning, cooking, and construction, but they are also capable of learning and adapting to new situations. Humans, on the other hand, are valued for their creativity and problem-solving abilities.

 The City of Rebots and Humans is a place of innovation, creativity, and mutual respect, where the boundaries between man and machine are blurred, and anything is possible. It is a shining example of what can be achieved when two very different species work together in harmony.
